# Exclude markdown from Prettier due to GitHub alerts incompatibility
# See: https://github.com/prettier/prettier/issues/15479
# 
# Prettier has known bugs with GitHub alerts (> [!NOTE], > [!WARNING], etc.)
# that cause them to be collapsed into single lines, breaking the alert rendering.
# 
# We use markdownlint-cli2 for markdown formatting instead, which properly
# supports GitHub Flavored Markdown extensions.

*.md
**/*.md
